<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Study Village</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Study Village</h1>
    <nav>
      <% if (currentUser) { %>
        <span><%= currentUser.nickname %>님 환영합니다</span>
        <a href="/room">학습방</a>
        <a href="/records">내 기록</a>
        <a href="/auth/logout">로그아웃</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/auth/login">로그인</a>
        <a href="/auth/register">회원가입</a>
      <% } %>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <p>웹 기반 공동 학습 서비스입니다.</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
